data.description: Large five bedroom 3 bath home with 3 car garage on 5.66 acres of beautiful land. Peaceful area. Home is over 3,000 square feet. This diamond in the rough features a kitchen with SS appliances that is open to the eating area. Skylights in both den and primary bedroom. Spacious den with wood burning fireplace has windows looking out to the covered patio. Built in's throughout. Home has radiant barrier in attic and roof turbines. Listing includes two plats of land. This home will need some TLC to make it your own.
